I can get rid of this and change OrcBatchPageSourceFactory and OrcSelectivePageSourceFactory to the following:
Map<Integer, Slice> keyMap = ImmutableMap.of();
if (encryptionInformation.isPresent() and encryptionInformation.getDwrfEncryptionMetadata.isPresent()
{
    keyMap = encryptionInformation.getDwrfEncryptionInformation.toKeyMap();
}

